       <span></span> 
       <a style="width:600px; height:30px; overflow:hidden;">英文一般般，怎么跟孩子阅读英文绘本？</a> 
      </div> 
      <div style="width:845px;"> 
       <div class="p10"> 
        <div class="fl">
         <img src="/Public/home/img/head_pic/head_boy_120.png" class="show_user_tab_42180 br5" height="90px" width="90px" />
        </div> 
        <div class="fl ml20" style="width:440px;"> 
         <div class="show_user_tab_ mb10"> 
